1️⃣ Pod/Deployment
Tumhare kube-state-metrics Deployment/Pod me hota hai label:
labels:
  app.kubernetes.io/name: kube-state-metrics
Ye label define karta hai ki Service kaunse pods ko target karega.

2️⃣ Service
Tumhare Service me hota hai selector:
selector:
  app.kubernetes.io/name: kube-state-metrics
Selector = Deployment/Pod ke labels se match karna chahiye
Ye decide karta hai ki service metrics request ko kaunse pods me forward kare

3️⃣ ServiceMonitor (Prometheus Operator ke liye)
Tumhare ServiceMonitor ka selector:
selector:
  matchLabels:
    app.kubernetes.io/name: kube-state-metrics
Ye Service ke labels se match karna chahiye, nahi toh Prometheus service ko scrape nahi karega

🔹 Flow me matching
Pod/Deployment label
      ↓ matches
Service selector
      ↓ matches
ServiceMonitor selector
      ↓ tells Prometheus to scrape this service



Kube-state-metrics + ServiceMonitor + PrometheusRule

Sab alerting aur metrics YAMLs alag hain:
kube-state-metrics Deployment + Service (automatically Helm se create hota hai)
ServiceMonitor → manually create, Prometheus ko metrics scrape karne ke liye
PrometheusRule → manually create, microservice A/B ke thresholds define karne ke liye
